msgid "Getting started"
msgstr "Kom i gang"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"            A new semester is available, <a href=\"%(url)s\">click here</a> "
"to get started.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            Et nytt semester er nå tilgjengelig, <a href=\"%(url)s\">klikk "
"her</a> for å komme igang.\n"
"          "

msgid ""
"\n"
"              Please enter a short name identifying your personal\n"
"              timetable, ie. username, nickname etc. If the name\n"
"              you select is in already taken, choose another\n"
"              one.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Oppgi et kort navn for timeplanen din\n"
"                (f.eks. et brukernavn eller kallenavn). \n"
"                Finn på et annet om det allerede er tatt.\n"
"              "

msgid "Start"
msgstr "Start"

msgid ""
"\n"
"          To retrieve your timetable simply enter the same identifier\n"
"          you used last time.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            Hent en timeplan ved å oppgi samme navnet som da du             "
"opprettet den.\n"
"          "

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Top %(limit)s courses %(current)s\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            Topp %(limit)s emner for %(current)s\n"
"          "

msgid "No courses have been added to any schedules yet."
msgstr "Ingen timeplaner er opprettet enda."

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Statistics %(current)s\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Statistikk for %(current)s\n"
"  "

msgid "Total number of unique timetables"
msgstr "Antall unike timeplaner"

msgid "Total number of unique courses added"
msgstr "Antall unike emner lagt til"

msgid ""
"Multiple courses can be added at once by separating course codes with spaces."
msgstr ""
"Legg til flere emner samtidig ved å skrive inn emnekoder adskilt med "
"mellomrom."

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"          For quick access to your schedule simply go to\n"
"          <a href=\"%(shortcut_url)s\">%(host)s%(shortcut_url)s</a>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Visste du at du alltid finner timeplanen din på: \n"
"        <a href=\"%(shortcut_url)s\">%(host)s%(shortcut_url)s</a>\n"
"      "

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Did you know that you can choose to hide lectures that you don't "
"want to be shown under\n"
"          <a href=\"%(adavanced_url)s\">advanced options</a>?\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Visste du at du kan skjule forelesninger under\n"
"        <a href=\"%(adavanced_url)s\">avanserte innstillinger</a>?\n"
"      "

msgid ""
"\n"
"          Did you know that you can select which groups (paralleller) you\n"
"          want to attend, and than you can select more than one group?\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Visste du at du kan velge hvilken parallell du tilhører,\n"
"        og at du kan velge mer enn én?\n"
"      "

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Did you know that you can change which names are used for courses "
"under\n"
"          <a href=\"%(adavanced_url)s\">advanced options</a>?\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Visste du at du kan endre visningsnavn på emner under\n"
"        <a href=\"%(adavanced_url)s\">avanserte innstillinger</a>?\n"
"       "

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Calendar export:\n"
"          <a href=\"%(ical_lectures_url)s\">lectures</a>,\n"
"          <a href=\"%(ical_exams_url)s\">exams</a> or\n"
"          <a href=\"%(ical_all_url)s\">both combined</a>.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"         Eksporter kalenderfil:\n"
"         <a href=\"%(ical_lectures_url)s\">forelesninger</a>,\n"
"         <a href=\"%(ical_exams_url)s\">eksamener</a> eller\n"
"         <a href=\"%(ical_all_url)s\">begge kombinert</a>.\n"
"      "

msgid ""
"Simply download or copy the link to the calendar you want and add it to any "
"application that supports the Ical format."
msgstr ""
"Last ned eller bruk lenken i valgfritt kalendersystem. (Må støtte ical-"
"formatet)."

msgid "Google calendar:"
msgstr "Google kalender:"

msgid "or"
msgstr "eller"

msgid "both combined"
msgstr "begge kombinert"

msgid ""
"Simply click the calendar type you want and it will be added to Google "
"calendar."
msgstr "Klikk lenken for å legge til i din Google Calendar."

